476
00:30:34,840 --> 00:30:35,720
Berbaliklah.

477
00:30:36,480 --> 00:30:37,330
Berbaliklah!

478
00:30:45,000 --> 00:30:47,560
Kepala Sekolah, Anda memiliki wibawa yang begitu besar
di akademi ini,

479
